            "date": 1750942965627,
            "name": "Commit-0",
            "content": "<header>\r\n    <nav>\r\n        <a routerLink=\"/\">Inicio</a>\r\n        <a routerLink=\"/productos\">Productos</a>\r\n        <a routerLink=\"/nosotros\">Nosotros</a>\r\n        <a routerLink=\"/contacto\">Contacto</a>\r\n        <div class=\"carrito-container\">\r\n            <button class=\"carrito-btn\" (click)=\"mostrarCarrito = !mostrarCarrito\">\r\n                🛒 <span class=\"carrito-cantidad\">{{ totalItems }}</span>\r\n            </button>\r\n            <div class=\"carrito-dropdown\" *ngIf=\"mostrarCarrito\">\r\n                <div *ngIf=\"cartService.getCart().length === 0\">El carrito está vacío</div>\r\n                <div *ngFor=\"let item of cartService.getCart()\">\r\n                    <span>{{item.producto.nombre}}</span>\r\n                    <button (click)=\"cartService.removeFromCart(item.producto)\">-</button>\r\n                    <span>{{item.cantidad}}</span>\r\n                    <button (click)=\"cartService.addToCart(item.producto)\">+</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div *ngIf=\"cartService.getCart().length > 0\">\r\n                    <strong>Total: ${{ cartService.getTotalPrice() }}</strong>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </nav>\r\n</header>\r\n"
